utbol|accessdate=20 June 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Cruz Azul]]\n|{{flagicon|Mexico}}\n| 28 November 2016\n| 27 November 2017\n{{WDL|48|17|18|13|for=56|against=52|diff=yes}}\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://laaficion.milenio.com/cruzazul/paco_jemez-cruz_azul-liga_mx-milenio-la_aficion_0_854914665.html|title=Paco J\u00e9mez, nuevo director t\u00e9cnico de Cruz Azul|trans-title=Paco J\u00e9mez, new technical director of Cruz Azul|newspaper=[[Milenio]]|first=Eduardo|last=Espinosa|language=Spanish|date=28 November 2016|accessdate=4 January 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[UD Las Palmas|Las Palmas]]\n|{{flagicon|Spain}}\n| 21 December 2017\n| 25 May 2018\n{{WDL|23|2|6|15|for=12|against=41|diff=yes}}\t\t\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bdfutbol.com/en/p/l816.html?temp=2017-18|title=Paco J\u00e9mez: Francisco J\u00e9mez Mart\u00edn: Matches 2017\u201318|publisher=BDFutbol|accessdate=23 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Rayo Vallecano]]\n|{{flagicon|Spain}}\n| 20 March 2019\n| ''Present''\n{{WDL|44|12|20|12|for=54|against=55|diff=yes}}\t\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bdfutbol.com/en/p/l816.html?temp=2018-19|title=Paco J\u00e9mez: Francisco J\u00e9mez Mart\u00edn: Matches 2018\u201319|publisher=BDFutbol|accessdate=20 March 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=https://www.bdfutbol.com/en/p/l816.html?temp=2019-20|title=Paco J\u00e9mez: Francisco J\u00e9mez Mart\u00edn: Matches 2019\u201320|publisher=BDFutbol|accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\t\n|-\n!colspan=\"4\"|Total\n{{WDLtot|435|139|127|169|for=541|against=662|diff=yes}}\t\n!\u2014\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n===Player===\n'''Deportivo'''\n*[[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]]: [[1995 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|1995]]\n\n'''Zaragoza'''\n*[[Copa del Rey]]: [[2000\u201301 Copa del Rey|2000\u201301]]<ref name=ABC/>\n\n===Manager===\n'''Cartagena'''\n*[[Segunda Divisi\u00f3n B]]: [[2008\u201309 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n B|2008\u201309]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{BDFutbol|816}}\n* {{BDFutbol ma